msgid "Compliance with Brazilian e-invoicing regulations"
msgstr "Naleving van Braziliaanse e-facturatieregels"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/brazil.rst:31
msgid ""
"Odoo Invoicing simplifies the process of adhering to Brazil’s complex e-"
