"normen van Hongarije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/hungary.rst:11
msgid "Legal framework for e-invoicing in Hungary"
msgstr "Wettelijk kader voor elektronische facturatie in Hongarije"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/hungary.rst:13
msgid ""
"In Hungary, businesses must adhere to e-invoicing regulations to ensure "
"secure, authentic, and storable transactions. The primary legal framework is "
"the Hungarian VAT Act (Act CXXVII of 2007), which mandates real-time "
"reporting of invoices to the NAV Online invoice system, Hungary's government "
"e-invoicing platform. As of 2021, all B2B and B2C invoices must be reported "
"in real-time, regardless of value. Hungary's regulations do not currently "
"require :abbr:`B2G (business-to-government)` e-invoicing, but public sector "
"invoicing is encouraged via the Peppol network. Common formats for e-"
"invoicing include XML for NAV submissions and other structured formats to "
"streamline compliance."
msgstr ""
"In Hongarije moeten bedrijven zich houden aan e-facturatieregels om veilige, "
"authentieke en opgeslagen transacties te waarborgen. Het primaire juridische "
"kader is de Hongaarse btw-wet (Wet CXXVII van 2007), die realtime rapportage "
"van verkoopfacturen aan het NAV Online-factuursysteem verplicht stelt, het e-"
"facturatieplatform van de Hongaarse overheid. Vanaf 2021 moeten alle B2B- en "
"B2C-verkoopfacturen realtime worden gerapporteerd, ongeacht de waarde. De "
"Hongaarse regelgeving vereist momenteel geen :abbr:`B2G (business-to-"
"government)`-e-facturatie, maar facturatie in de overheidssector wordt "
"aangemoedigd via het Peppol-netwerk. Veelgebruikte formaten voor e-"
"facturatie zijn onder andere XML voor NAV-inzendingen en andere "
"gestructureerde formaten om naleving te stroomlijnen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/hungary.rst:23
msgid "Compliance with Hungarian e-invoicing regulations"
msgstr "Naleving van Hongaarse e-facturatieregels"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/hungary.rst:25
msgid ""
"Odoo invoicing module is designed to help businesses meet Hungary's e-"
"invoicing and VAT reporting requirements. Here is how Odoo ensures "
"compliance:"
msgstr ""
"De Odoo-facturatiemodule is ontworpen om bedrijven te helpen voldoen aan de "
"e-facturatie- en btw-rapportagevereisten van Hongarije. Zo waarborgt Odoo "
"naleving:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/hungary.rst:28
msgid ""
"**Supported Formats**: Odoo supports the standardized XML format required "
"for integration with the NAV (Nemzeti Adó és Vámhivatal) Online Invoice "
"System, ensuring seamless real-time invoice reporting. The module also "
"supports formats compatible with Peppol for cross-border transactions, "
"promoting compliance with EU e-invoicing standards. Odoo enables businesses "
"to automatically report invoices to the Hungarian tax authorities in real-"
"time, as required by law."
msgstr ""
"**Ondersteunde formaten**: Odoo ondersteunt het gestandaardiseerde XML-"
"formaat dat vereist is voor integratie met het NAV (Nemzeti Adó és "
"Vámhivatal) Online-factuursysteem, en zorgt voor naadloze realtime "
"facturatierapportage. De module ondersteunt ook formaten die compatibel zijn "
"met Peppol voor grensoverschrijdende transacties, en bevordert naleving van "
"EU-e-facturatienormen. Odoo stelt bedrijven in staat om automatisch "
"verkoopfacturen realtime te rapporteren aan de Hongaarse "
"belastingautoriteiten, zoals wettelijk vereist."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/hungary.rst:33
msgid ""
"**Secure storage and retrieval**: In accordance with Hungarian regulations, "
"which mandate storing invoices for a minimum of eight years, Odoo securely "
"archives all invoices in a tamper-proof system, allowing for easy retrieval "
"during audits."
msgstr ""
"**Veilige opslag en ophalen**: In overeenstemming met Hongaarse regelgeving, "
"die verplicht verkoopfacturen minimaal acht jaar te bewaren, archiveert Odoo "
"alle verkoopfacturen veilig in een fraudebestendig systeem, waardoor ze "
"gemakkelijk kunnen worden opgehaald tijdens audits."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/hungary.rst:36
msgid ""
"**Automatic VAT calculation and reporting**: Odoo Invoicing automates VAT "
"calculations and ensures invoices meet the strict requirements of the "
"Hungarian VAT Act, simplifying compliance for B2B and B2C transactions."
msgstr ""
"**Automatische btw-berekening en rapportage**: Odoo Facturatie automatiseert "
"btw-berekeningen en zorgt ervoor dat verkoopfacturen voldoen aan de strikte "
"vereisten van de Hongaarse btw-wet, waardoor naleving voor B2B- en B2C-"
"transacties wordt vereenvoudigd."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/hungary.rst:42
msgid ""
"This page provides an overview of Hungarian e-invoicing laws and how Odoo "
