#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:3
msgid "Multi-currency system"
msgstr "Multivalutasysteem"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo allows you to issue invoices, receive bills, and record transactions in "
"currencies other than the main currency configured for your company. You can "
"also set up bank accounts in other currencies and run reports on your "
"foreign currency activities."
msgstr ""
"Met Odoo kun je verkoopfacturen versturen, leveranciersfacturen ontvangen en "
"transacties registreren in andere valuta dan de hoofdvaluta die voor je "
"bedrijf is geconfigureerd. Je kunt ook bankrekeningen in andere valuta "
"instellen en rapporten over je buitenlandse valuta-activiteiten uitvoeren."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:10
msgid ":doc:`../bank/foreign_currency`"
msgstr ":doc:`../bank/foreign_currency`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:20
msgid "Main currency"
msgstr "Hoofdvaluta"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:22
msgid ""
"The **main currency** is defined by default according to the company's "
"country. You can change it by going to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Settings --> Currencies` and changing the currency in "
"the :guilabel:`Main Currency` setting."
msgstr ""
"De **hoofdvaluta** wordt standaard bepaald op basis van het land van het "
"bedrijf. Je kunt deze wijzigen door naar :menuselection:`Boekhouding --> "
"Configuratie --> Instellingen --> Valuta` te gaan en de valuta te wijzigen "
"in de instelling :guilabel:`Hoofdvaluta`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:29
msgid "Enable foreign currencies"
msgstr "Schakel buitenlandse valuta in"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:31
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Currencies`, and "
"enable the currencies you wish to use by toggling the :guilabel:`Active` "
"button."
msgstr ""
"Ga naar :menuselection:`Boekhouding --> Configuratie --> Valuta` en activeer "
"de valuta die je wilt gebruiken door de knop :guilabel:`Actief` in te "
"schakelen."

