#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:3
msgid "SEPA Direct Debit (SDD) customer payments"
msgstr "Klantbetalingen via SEPA-domiciliëring (SDD)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:7
msgid ""
"SEPA (Single Euro Payments Area) is a payment-integration initiative of the "
"European Union that facilitates standardized and simplified electronic "
"payments in euros across participating countries. With **SEPA Direct Debit** "
"(SDD), customers sign a mandate that authorizes you to collect future "
"payments from their bank accounts. This is particularly useful for recurring "
"payments based on a :doc:`subscription </applications/sales/subscriptions>`."
msgstr ""
"SEPA (Single Euro Payments Area) is een betalingsintegratie-initiatief van "
"de Europese Unie dat gestandaardiseerde en vereenvoudigde elektronische "
"betalingen in euro's vergemakkelijkt in deelnemende landen. Met **SEPA-"
"domiciliëring** (SDD) ondertekenen klanten een machtiging die jou "
"toestemming geeft om toekomstige betalingen van hun bankrekeningen te innen. "
"Dit is vooral handig voor terugkerende betalingen op basis van een "
":doc:`abonnement </applications/sales/subscriptions>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:13
msgid ""
"You can record customer |sdd| mandates in Odoo and generate XML files "
"listing payments to be collected with the mandates. :ref:`Uploading these "
"files to your bank <accounting/batch_sdd/XML>` instructs them to collect "
"these payments from your customers."
msgstr ""
"Je kunt |sdd|-machtigingen van klanten vastleggen in Odoo en XML-bestanden "
"genereren met een lijst van betalingen die met de machtigingen moeten worden "
"geïnd. :ref:`Deze bestanden uploaden naar je bank <accounting/batch_sdd/XML>"
"` geeft hen de opdracht om deze betalingen van je klanten te innen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:18
msgid ""
"|sdd| is supported by all SEPA countries, which includes the 27 member "
"states of the European Union as well as additional countries."
msgstr ""
"|sdd| wordt ondersteund door alle SEPA-landen, waaronder de 27 lidstaten van "
"de Europese Unie en enkele andere landen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:20
msgid ""
"`List of all SEPA countries <https://www.europeanpaymentscouncil.eu/document-"
"library/other/epc-list-sepa-scheme-countries>`_."
msgstr ""
"`Lijst van alle SEPA-landen <https://www.europeanpaymentscouncil.eu/document-"
"library/other/epc-list-sepa-scheme-countries>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:29
msgid "Creditor identifier"
msgstr "Crediteur-ID"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:31
msgid ""
"To enable |sdd| for customer payments, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, scroll to the :guilabel:`Customer Payments` "
"section, enable :guilabel:`SEPA Direct Debit (SDD)`, and "
"click :guilabel:`Save`. Then, scroll to the :guilabel:`Customer Payments` "
"section again, set the company's :guilabel:`Creditor Identifier`, and "
"click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Schakel |sdd| in voor klantbetalingen door naar "
":menuselection:`Boekhouding --> Configuratie --> Instellingen` te gaan, "
"scroll naar de sectie :guilabel:`Klantbetalingen`, schakel :guilabel:`SEPA-"
"domiciliëring (SDD)` in en klik op :guilabel:`Opslaan`. Scroll vervolgens "
"opnieuw naar de sectie :guilabel:`Klantbetalingen`, stel de "
":guilabel:`Crediteur-ID` van het bedrijf in en klik op :guilabel:`Opslaan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:37
msgid ""
"The creditor identifier is provided by your bank or the authority "
"responsible for delivering them in your country. For testing purposes, you "
"can use the test creditor identifier `DE98ZZZ09999999999`."
msgstr ""
"De crediteur-ID wordt verstrekt door je bank of de autoriteit die "
"verantwoordelijk is voor het uitgeven ervan in jouw land. Voor "
"testdoeleinden kun je de test crediteur-ID `DE98ZZZ09999999999` gebruiken."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:42
msgid "PAIN file version"
msgstr "PAIN-bestandsversie"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:44
msgid ""
"By default, the :ref:`SEPA-compliant XML files <accounting/batch_sdd/XML>` "
"generated by Odoo use the |sdd| **PAIN.008.001.02** format. If your bank "
"requires the updated 2023 version, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Journals` and select the :guilabel:`Bank` journal. Then, "
"in the :guilabel:`Incoming Payments` tab, set the :guilabel:`SEPA Pain "
"version` field to :guilabel:`Updated 2023 (Pain 008.001.08)`."
msgstr ""
"Standaard gebruiken de :ref:`SEPA-conforme XML-bestanden <accounting/"
"batch_sdd/XML>` die door Odoo worden gegenereerd het |sdd| "
"**PAIN.008.001.02**-formaat. Als je bank de bijgewerkte versie van 2023 "
"vereist, ga dan naar :menuselection:`Boekhouding --> Configuratie --> "
"Dagboeken` en selecteer het :guilabel:`Bank`-dagboek. Stel vervolgens op het "
"tabblad :guilabel:`Inkomende betalingen` het veld :guilabel:`SEPA Pain-"
"versie` in op :guilabel:`Bijgewerkt 2023 (Pain 008.001.08)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:51
msgid ""
"`SEPA Direct Debit Core Customer-to-PSP Implementation Guidelines <https://"
"www.europeanpaymentscouncil.eu/document-library/implementation-guidelines/"
"sepa-direct-debit-core-customer-psp-implementation-0>`_."
msgstr ""
"`SEPA Direct Debit Core Customer-to-PSP Implementation Guidelines <https://"
"www.europeanpaymentscouncil.eu/document-library/implementation-guidelines/"
"sepa-direct-debit-core-customer-psp-implementation-0>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:57
msgid "SEPA Direct Debit Mandates"
msgstr "SEPA Automatische Incasso Mandaten"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:59
msgid ""
"An |sdd| mandate is a legal document authorizing a company to debit funds "
"from a customer's bank account. It includes key information, such as the "
"customer's name and IBAN, the mandate's start and end date, and the "
"mandate's unique identifier. The mandate form must be filled in and signed "
"by the customer."
msgstr ""
"Een |sdd|-machtiging is een juridisch document dat een bedrijf toestemming "
"geeft om geld af te schrijven van de bankrekening van een klant. Het bevat "
"belangrijke informatie, zoals de naam en IBAN van de klant, de begin- en "
"einddatum van de machtiging en de unieke ID van de machtiging. Het "
"machtigingsformulier moet worden ingevuld en ondertekend door de klant."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:65
msgid "Creating mandates"
msgstr "Machtigingen aanmaken"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:67
msgid "To create an |sdd| mandate:"
msgstr "Een |sdd|-machtiging aanmaken:"

