#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:101
msgid ""
"The contact information on the invoice or the contact form is used to send "
"the reminder."
msgstr ""
"De contactinformatie op de factuur of het contactformulier wordt gebruikt om "
"de herinnering te versturen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:102
msgid "The chatter keeps a full record of all follow-up actions."
msgstr ""
"De chatter houdt een volledig overzicht bij van alle acties voor "
"betalingsherinneringen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:107
msgid "Follow-ups for all customers due for action"
msgstr "Betaalherinneringen voor alle klanten die actie vereisen"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:109
msgid ""
"After setting up the additional :ref:`follow-up <accounting/follow_up/follow-"
"ups-for-one-customer>` options, review which customers have overdue invoices "
"or require follow-up. To do so, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Customers --> Customers`. In the :guilabel:`Customers` kanban view, click "
"the search bar and filter by :guilabel:`Overdue Invoices` "
"or :guilabel:`Requires Follow-up`."
msgstr ""
"Nadat je de aanvullende :ref:`betaalherinneringen <accounting/follow_up/"
"follow-ups-for-one-customer>`-opties hebt ingesteld, bekijk je welke klanten "
"achterstallige verkoopfacturen hebben of opvolging vereisen. Ga hiervoor "
"naar :menuselection:`Boekhouding --> Klanten --> Klanten`. Klik in de "
":guilabel:`Klanten`-kanban-weergave op de zoekbalk en filter op "
":guilabel:`Achterstallige verkoopfacturen` of :guilabel:`Vereist opvolging`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:115
msgid ""
"To take follow-up actions for all relevant customers, switch to the list "
"view and select the customers requiring follow-up. Then, click :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`(Actions)` and select :guilabel:`Process Follow-ups` to send "
"them the :ref:`follow-up report <accounting/follow_up/follow-up-report>`."
msgstr ""
"Om betaalherinneringsacties voor alle relevante klanten te ondernemen, "
"schakel je over naar de lijstweergave en selecteer je de klanten die "
"opvolging vereisen. Klik vervolgens op :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(Acties)` "
"en selecteer :guilabel:`Betaalherinneringen verwerken` om hen het "
":ref:`betaalherinneringsrapport <accounting/follow_up/follow-up-report>` te "
"sturen."

