#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_checks.rst:35
msgid "**Peachtree**: check in the middle, stubs on top and bottom;"
msgstr "**Peachtree**: cheque in het midden, strooken bovenaan en onderaan;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_checks.rst:36
msgid "**ADP**: check in the bottom, and stubs on the top."
msgstr "**ADP**: cheque onderaan en stubs bovenaan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_checks.rst:39
msgid "Pay a supplier bill with a check"
msgstr "Betaal een leveranciersfactuur met een cheque"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_checks.rst:41
msgid "Paying a supplier with a check is done in three steps:"
msgstr "Een leverancier betalen met een cheque gebeurd in drie stappen:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_checks.rst:43
msgid "registering a payment"
msgstr "een betaling registreren"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_checks.rst:44
msgid "printing checks in batch for all registered payments"
msgstr "Checks in batch afdrukken voor alle geregistreerde betalingen"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_checks.rst:45
msgid "reconciling bank statements"
msgstr "bankafschriften afletteren"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_checks.rst:48
msgid "Register a payment by check"
msgstr "Registreer een betaling via cheque"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_checks.rst:50
msgid ""
"To register a payment, open any supplier bill from the "
"menu :menuselection:`Purchases --> Vendor Bills`. Once the supplier bill is "
"validated, you can register a payment. Set the :guilabel:`Payment Method` "
"to :guilabel:`Checks` and validate the payment."
msgstr ""
"Registreer een betaling door een leveranciersfactuur te openen via het menu "
":menuselection:`Inkoop --> Leveranciersfacturen`. Zodra de "
"leveranciersfactuur is gevalideerd, kun je een betaling registreren. Stel de "
":guilabel:`Betaalmethode` in op :guilabel:`Cheques` en valideer de betaling."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_checks.rst:56
msgid "Print checks"
msgstr "Print cheques"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_checks.rst:58
msgid ""
"On your :guilabel:`Accounting Dashboard` in the :guilabel:`Bank` Journal, "
"you can see the number of checks registered. By clicking "
"on :guilabel:`Checks to print` you have got the possibility to print the "
"reconciled checks."
msgstr ""
"Op je :guilabel:`Boekhouding-dashboard` in het :guilabel:`Bank`dagboek zie "
"je het aantal geregistreerde cheques. Door op :guilabel:`Af te drukken "
"cheques` te klikken, kun je de afgeletterde cheques afdrukken."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_checks.rst:62
msgid ""
"To print all checks in batch, select all payments from the list view and "
"click on :guilabel:`Print`."
msgstr ""
"Selecteer alle betalingen in de lijstweergave en klik op "
":guilabel:`Afdrukken` om alle cheques in batch af te drukken."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_sepa.rst:3
msgid "Pay with SEPA"
msgstr "Betaal met SEPA"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_sepa.rst:5
msgid ""
"SEPA, the Single Euro Payments Area, is a payment-integration initiative of "
"the European Union to simplify bank transfers denominated in euros. SEPA "
"allows you to send payment orders to your bank to automate bank wire "
"transfers."
msgstr ""
"SEPA, de gemeenschappelijke eurobetalingsruimte, is een betalingsintegratie-"
"initiatief van de Europese Unie om bankoverschrijvingen in euro's te "
"vereenvoudigen. Met SEPA kun je betalingsopdrachten naar je bank sturen om "
"bankoverschrijvingen te automatiseren."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_sepa.rst:9
msgid "SEPA is supported by the banks of the 27 EU member states, as well as:"
msgstr "SEPA wordt ondersteund door de banken van de 27 EU-lidstaten, evenals:"

