msgstr ""
"Leveranciersfacturen worden :ref:`handmatig geüpload <accounting/bill-"
"digitization/manual-upload>` of verzonden naar een :ref:`aangewezen e-"
"mailalias <accounting/bill-digitization/email-alias>` om te worden "
"gedigitaliseerd. Ze kunnen ook :ref:`automatisch worden geboekt <accounting/"
"bill-digitization/auto-post-bills>` voor geselecteerde leveranciers."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:45
msgid ""
"Once the bill is uploaded, the document preview appears on the right side of "
"the screen."
msgstr ""
"Zodra de factuur is geüpload, verschijnt het documentvoorbeeld aan de "
"rechterkant van het scherm."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:48
msgid ":doc:`Vendor bills <../vendor_bills>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Leveranciersfacturen <../vendor_bills>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:53
msgid "Manual upload"
msgstr "Handmatig uploaden"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:55
msgid ""
"In the Accounting dashboard, drag and drop vendor bills into the desired "
