"selecteer het :guilabel:`Bank`-dagboek. Voer het :guilabel:`Rekeningnummer` "
"in, klik op :guilabel:`Aanmaken en bewerken...` en vul de volgende velden in:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:422
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:452
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:249
msgid ":guilabel:`Bank`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Bank`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:423
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:453
msgid ":guilabel:`BSB`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`BSB`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:424
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:454
msgid ":guilabel:`Account Holder`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Rekeninghouder`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:426
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:456
msgid ""
"Then, toggle on the :guilabel:`Send Money` switch and click :guilabel:`Save "
"& Close`."
msgstr ""
"Schakel vervolgens de schakelaar :guilabel:`Geld verzenden` in en klik op "
":guilabel:`Opslaan & sluiten`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:429
msgid "Using the :guilabel:`Currency` field is optional."
msgstr "Het gebruik van het veld :guilabel:`Valuta` is optioneel."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:431
msgid ""
"Back on the :guilabel:`Journal Entries` tab, fill in the following fields "
"under the :guilabel:`ABA` section:"
msgstr ""
"Ga terug naar het tabblad :guilabel:`Boekingen` en vul de volgende velden in "
"onder de sectie :guilabel:`ABA`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:434
msgid ""
":guilabel:`BSB`: the BSB code from the bank account is used to fill in this "
"field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`BSB`: de BSB-code van de bankrekening wordt gebruikt om dit veld "
"in te vullen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:435
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Financial Institution Code`: the official 3-letter abbreviation "
"of the bank (e.g., `WBC` for Westpac)"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Code van de financiële instelling`: de officiële afkorting van "
"drie letters van de bank (bv. `WBC` voor Westpac)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:437
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Supplying User Name`: 6-digit number provided by the bank. "
"Contact your bank or check its website if you do not know it."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Gebruikersnaam van de leverancier`: zescijferig nummer verstrekt "
"door de bank. Neem contact op met je bank of raadpleeg de website als je dit "
"nummer niet weet."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:439
msgid ""
":guilabel:`APCA Identification Number`: 6-digit number provided by the bank. "
"Contact your bank or check its website if you do not know it."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`APCA-identificatienummer`: zescijferig nummer verstrekt door de "
"bank. Neem contact op met je bank of raadpleeg de website als je dit nummer "
"niet weet."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:442
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Include Self Balancing Transaction`: selecting this option adds "
"an additional"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Zelfbalancerende transactie opnemen`: deze optie selecteren voegt "
"een extra"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:442
msgid ""
"\"self-balancing\" transaction to the end of the ABA file, which is required "
"by some banks."
msgstr ""
"\"zelfbalancerende\" transactie toe aan het einde van het ABA-bestand, wat "
"door sommige banken vereist is."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:445
msgid "Customers' and vendors' bank accounts"
