msgstr "De verbinding configureren"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:340
msgid "For companies"
msgstr "Voor bedrijven"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:343
msgid ""
"Make sure the :doc:`company settings </applications/general/companies>` are "
"correctly configured, i.e., the country is set to :guilabel:`Belgium` and "
"the :guilabel:`Tax ID` or :guilabel:`Company ID` field is filled."
msgstr ""
"Zorg ervoor dat de :doc:`bedrijfsinstellingen </applications/general/"
"companies>` correct zijn, d.w.z. dat het land is ingesteld op "
":guilabel:`België` en het veld :guilabel:`Btw-nummer` of :guilabel:`Bedrijfs-"
"ID` is ingevuld."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:347
