msgstr ""
"Factuurstatuscontrole (1 credit wordt verbruikt telkens wanneer de "
"factuurstatus wordt gecontroleerd)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:390
msgid ""
"If taxes are calculated in the **Sales** app and the invoice is later issued "
"in the **Accounting** app, the calculation happens twice, consuming two "
"credits."
msgstr ""
"Als btw wordt berekend in de **Verkoop**-app en de factuur later wordt "
"uitgegeven in de **Boekhouding**-app, vindt de berekening twee keer plaats "
"en worden er twee credits verbruikt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:404
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Service Code Origin`: City Service Code where the provider is "
"registered"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Herkomst servicecode`: Gemeentelijke servicecode waar de provider "
"is geregistreerd"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:405
