msgstr ""
"**SRI**: *Servicio de Rentas Internas*, de overheidsorganisatie die de "
"betaling van belastingen in Ecuador handhaaft."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:24
msgid ""
"**SRI certificate**: Document or digital credential issued by the *SRI* that "
