msgid ""
":guilabel:`Customer withholdings` are non-electronic documents issued by the "
"client to apply a withholding to a sale. They can only be registered from a "
"validated (posted) invoice."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Bronbelastingen voor klanten` zijn niet-elektronische documenten "
