#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/hungary.rst:40
msgid ""
"The Hungarian localization package offers key features and integration "
"capabilities that ensure compliance with local fiscal and accounting "
"regulations. The package includes tools for managing taxes, fiscal "
"positions, reporting, and a predefined chart of accounts tailored to "
"Hungarian authorities' standards."
msgstr ""
"Het Hongaarse lokalisatiepakket biedt belangrijke functies en "
"integratiemogelijkheden die naleving van lokale fiscale en boekhoudkundige "
"regelgeving waarborgen. Het pakket bevat tools voor het beheren van btw, "
"fiscale posities, rapportage en een voorgedefinieerd grootboekschema dat is "
"afgestemd op de normen van de Hongaarse autoriteiten."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/hungary.rst:45
msgid ""
":doc:`../accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts`: a predefined structure "
"tailored to Hungarian accounting standards."
msgstr ""
":doc:`../accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts`: een voorgedefinieerde "
"structuur afgestemd op Hongaarse boekhoudnormen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/hungary.rst:47
msgid ""
":ref:`localizations/hungary/taxes`: pre-configured tax rates, including "
"standard VAT, compensatory surcharge, zero-rated, and exempt options."
msgstr ""
":ref:`localizations/hungary/taxes`: vooraf geconfigureerde btw-tarieven, "
"inclusief standaard btw, compenserende heffing, nul-tarief en vrijgestelde "
"opties."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/hungary.rst:49
msgid ""
":doc:`../accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions`: automated tax adjustments based "
"on customer or supplier registration status."
msgstr ""
":doc:`../accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions`: geautomatiseerde btw-"
"aanpassingen op basis van de registratiestatus van de klant of leverancier."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/hungary.rst:51
msgid ""
":ref:`localizations/hungary/tax-reporting`: detailed overview of your net "
"tax liability."
msgstr ""
":ref:`localizations/hungary/tax-reporting`: gedetailleerd overzicht van je "
"netto btw-verplichting."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/hungary.rst:52
msgid ""
":ref:`e-Invoicing <localizations/hungary/e-invoicing>`: integration for "
"electronic invoicing using NAV 3.0 (Online Számlá) in line with the National "
"Tax and Customs Administrations' requirements."
msgstr ""
":ref:`e-Facturatie <localizations/hungary/e-invoicing>`: integratie voor "
"elektronische facturatie met NAV 3.0 (Online Számlá) in lijn met de "
"vereisten van de Nationale Belasting- en Douane-administratie."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/hungary.rst:60
msgid ""
"The following :doc:`taxes <../accounting/taxes>` are available by default "
"with the Hungarian localization package:"
msgstr ""
"De volgende :doc:`btw <../accounting/taxes>` zijn standaard beschikbaar met "
"het Hongaarse lokalisatiepakket:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/hungary.rst:63
msgid ""
"Standard and Reduced VAT: standard sales tax (27%) and reduced rates (18% "
"and 5%) applied to goods and services in Hungary."
msgstr ""
"Standaard en verlaagde btw: standaard omzetbelasting (27%) en verlaagde "
"tarieven (18% en 5%) toegepast op goederen en diensten in Hongarije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/hungary.rst:65
msgid ""
"Agricultural Compensation Surcharge (7% or 12%): applied to specific "
"agricultural and livestock products."
msgstr ""
"Agrarische compensatieheffing (7% of 12%): toegepast op specifieke landbouw- "
"en veehouderijproducten."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/hungary.rst:67
msgid ""
"Intra-Community and Trade taxes: zero-rated (0%) and tax-exempt options "
"applied to EU intra-community sales, exports outside the EU, and domestic "
"exemptions."
msgstr ""
"Intracommunautaire en handelstarieven: nul-tarief (0%) en btw-vrijgestelde "
"opties toegepast op intracommunautaire verkopen binnen de EU, uitvoer buiten "
"de EU en binnenlandse vrijstellingen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/hungary.rst:73
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:73
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/luxembourg.rst:84
msgid "Tax reporting"
msgstr "Belastingrapportage"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/hungary.rst:75
msgid ""
"The :doc:`VAT summary <../accounting/reporting/tax_returns>` provides a "
"detailed breakdown of taxable, zero-rated, and exempt transactions. Like "
"other :doc:`financial reports <../accounting/reporting>`, the VAT summary "
"can be filtered by period, compared against other periods, and exported in "
"Excel and PDF formats, ensuring compliance with Hungarian tax laws."
msgstr ""
"De :doc:`btw-samenvatting <../accounting/reporting/tax_returns>` biedt een "
"gedetailleerde uitsplitsing van belastbare, nul-tarief en vrijgestelde "
"transacties. Net als andere :doc:`financiële rapporten <../accounting/"
"reporting>` kan de btw-samenvatting gefilterd worden per periode, vergeleken "
"worden met andere periodes en geëxporteerd worden in Excel- en pdf-formaten, "
"waardoor naleving van de Hongaarse belastingwetgeving wordt gewaarborgd."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/hungary.rst:83
