msgid "Document Types"
msgstr "Documenttypes"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:410
msgid ""
"The :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)` requires businesses to send "
"customer invoices and other documents through the :abbr:`EDI (Electronic "
"Data Interchange)`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:413
msgid ""
"The following :guilabel:`Document Type` codes all technically identify "
"different business use cases."
msgstr ""
"De volgende :guilabel:`Documenttype` codes identificeren technisch gezien "
"verschillende zakelijke use cases."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:418
msgid "TD01 - Invoices"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:420
msgid ""
"This represents the standard **domestic** scenario for all invoices "
"exchanged through the :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)`. Any invoice "
"that doesn't fall into one of the specific special cases is categorized as a "
"regular invoice, identified by the :guilabel:`Document Type` `TD01`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:427
msgid "TD02 - Down payments"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:429
msgid ""
"**Down payment** invoices are imported/exported with a "
"different :guilabel:`Document Type` code `TDO2` than regular invoices. Upon "
"import of the invoice, a regular vendor bill is created."
msgstr ""
"**Aanbetaling** verkoopfacturen worden geïmporteerd/geëxporteerd met een "
"andere :guilabel:`Documenttype` code `TDO2` dan reguliere verkoopfacturen. "
"Bij import van de verkoopfactuur wordt een reguliere leveranciersfactuur "
"aangemaakt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:432
msgid ""
"Odoo exports transactions as `TD02` if the following conditions are met:"
msgstr ""
"Odoo exporteert transacties als `TD02` als aan de volgende voorwaarden is "
"voldaan:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:434
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:574
msgid "It is an invoice;"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:435
msgid "All invoice lines are related to down payment sales order lines."
msgstr "Alle factuurregels zijn gerelateerd aan aanbetaling verkooporderregels."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:440
msgid "TD04 - Credit notes"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:442
msgid ""
"It is the standard scenario for all **credit notes** issued to **domestic** "
"clients, when we need to formally acknowledge that the seller is reducing or "
"cancelling a previously issued invoice, for example, in case of overbilling, "
"incorrect items, or overpayment. Just like invoices, they must be sent to "
"the :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)`, their :guilabel:`Document Type` "
"`TD04`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:450
msgid "TD07, TD08, TD09 - Simplified Invoicing"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:452
msgid ""
"Simplified invoices (`TD07`), credit notes (`TD08`), and debit notes "
"(`TD09`) can be used to certify domestic transactions under 400 EUR (VAT "
"included). Its status is the same as that of a regular invoice, but with "
"fewer information requirements."
msgstr ""
"Vereenvoudigde facturen (`TD07`), creditnota's (`TD08`) en debetnota's "
"(`TD09`) kunnen worden gebruikt om binnenlandse transacties onder de 400 EUR "
"(inclusief btw) te certificeren. De status is dezelfde als die van een "
"reguliere verkoopfactuur, maar met minder informatievereisten."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:456
msgid "For a simplified invoice to be established, it must include:"
msgstr "Stel een vereenvoudigde factuur op met de volgende elementen:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:458
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Customer Invoice` reference: **unique** numbering sequence with "
"**no gaps**;"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:459
msgid ":guilabel:`Invoice Date`: issue **date** of the invoice;"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:460
msgid ""
":ref:`Company Info <general/companies/company>`: the **seller**'s full "
"credentials (VAT/TIN number, name, full address);"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:462
msgid ":guilabel:`VAT`: the **buyer**'s VAT/TIN number (on the partner form);"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:463
msgid ":guilabel:`Total`: the total **amount** (VAT included) of the invoice."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Totaal`: het totale **bedrag** (inclusief btw) van de "
"verkoopfactuur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:465
msgid ""
"In the :abbr:`EDI (Electronic Data Interchange)`, Odoo exports invoices as "
"simplified if:"
msgstr ""
"In de :abbr:`EDI (elektronische gegevensuitwisseling)` exporteert Odoo "
"verkoopfacturen als vereenvoudigd indien:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:467
msgid "It is a domestic transaction (i.e., the partner is from Italy);"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:468
msgid ""
"Your company's **required fields** (:guilabel:`VAT Number` "
"or :guilabel:`Codice Fiscale`, :guilabel:`Fiscal Regime`, and full "
"**address**) are provided;"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:470
msgid ""
"The partner's address is not fully specified (i.e., it misses the City or "
"the ZipCode);"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:471
msgid "The total amount of VAT included is **less** than **400 EUR**."
msgstr "Het totale bedrag inclusief btw is **lager** dan **400 EUR**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:474
msgid ""
"The 400 EUR threshold was defined in `the decree of the 10th of May 2019 in "
"the Gazzetta Ufficiale <https://www.gazzettaufficiale.it/eli/id/"
"2019/05/24/19A03271/sg>`_. We advise you to check the current official value."
msgstr ""
"De drempelwaarde van 400 EUR werd gedefinieerd in `het decreet van 10 mei "
"2019 in de Gazzetta Ufficiale <https://www.gazzettaufficiale.it/eli/id/2019/"
"05/24/19A03271/sg>`_. We raden je aan de huidige officiële waarde te "
"controleren."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:481
msgid "TD16 - Internal Reverse Charge"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:483
msgid ""
