"Zodra het bedrijf :ref:`gekoppeld is met JoFotara <localizations/jordan/"
"linking-jofotara>` en het :ref:`bedrijf en de klanten correct zijn "
"geconfigureerd <localizations/jordan/company-and-contacts>`, kunnen "
"verkoopfacturen via Odoo naar JoFotara worden verzonden:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:181
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Send` window, select :guilabel:`JoFotara (Jordan EDI)` and "
"click :guilabel:`Send`."
msgstr ""
"Selecteer in het venster :guilabel:`Verzenden` de optie :guilabel:`JoFotara "
"(Jordanië EDI)` en klik op :guilabel:`Verzenden`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:184
msgid "When an invoice is sent to JoFotara, Odoo does the following:"
msgstr ""
"Wanneer een factuur naar JoFotara wordt verzonden, doet Odoo het volgende:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:186
msgid "generates the invoice in the required format (UBL 1.2)"
msgstr "genereert de factuur in het vereiste formaat (UBL 1.2)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:187
msgid "submits the invoice to JoFotara for validation"
msgstr "dient de factuur in bij JoFotara ter validatie"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:188
msgid "receives the QR code from JoFotara on the invoice's PDF"
msgstr "ontvangt de QR-code van JoFotara op de pdf van de factuur"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:191
msgid ""
"Multiple invoices can be :ref:`sent at once <accounting/invoice/sending>` to "
"JoFotara."
msgstr ""
"Meerdere verkoopfacturen kunnen :ref:`tegelijk verzonden <accounting/invoice/"
"sending>` worden naar JoFotara."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:192
msgid ""
"From the :guilabel:`Invoices` list view, filter the invoices by "
"their :ref:`localizations/jordan/jofotara-state` to see the invoices that "
"have either been sent or not been sent to JoFotara."
msgstr ""
"Vanuit de lijstweergave :guilabel:`Verkoopfacturen` kun je de "
"verkoopfacturen filteren op hun :ref:`localizations/jordan/jofotara-state` "
"om te zien welke verkoopfacturen wel of niet naar JoFotara zijn verzonden."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:195
msgid ""
"In the :icon:`oi-settings-adjust` (:guilabel:`adjust settings`) menu, add "
"the :guilabel:`JoFotara State` and :guilabel:`JoFotara Error` fields to see "
"the sending state and any errors in the list view, respectively."
msgstr ""
"Voeg in het menu :icon:`oi-settings-adjust` (:guilabel:`instellingen "
"aanpassen`) de velden :guilabel:`JoFotara-status` en :guilabel:`JoFotara-"
"fout` toe om respectievelijk de verzendstatus en eventuele fouten in de "
"lijstweergave te zien."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:200
msgid ""
"There is an inherent difference in how values are approximated in Odoo and "
"ISTD due to the differing system architectures. JOD values in Odoo are "
"stored and approximated to three decimals, whereas ISTD expects values to "
"have nine decimals. As a result, an insignificant difference is inevitable "
"and arises between the values stores in Odoo and the values reported to "
"ISTD, which can have an error margin of <0.001."
msgstr ""
"Er is een inherent verschil in hoe waarden worden afgerond in Odoo en ISTD "
"vanwege de verschillende systeemarchitecturen. JOD-waarden in Odoo worden "
"opgeslagen en afgerond op drie decimalen, terwijl ISTD waarden met negen "
"decimalen verwacht. Hierdoor is een onbeduidend verschil onvermijdelijk en "
"ontstaat er verschil tussen de waarden die in Odoo zijn opgeslagen en de "
"waarden die aan ISTD worden gerapporteerd, met een foutmarge van <0,001."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:209
msgid "JoFotara State"
msgstr "JoFotara-status"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:211
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`JoFotara State` field in the :guilabel:`Other Info` tab of "
"confirmed invoices reflects the current state of the document in JoFotara. "
"It can be changed manually to reflect the actual state of the invoices in "
"cases where a technical error or timeout prevents Odoo from updating it "
"automatically."
msgstr ""
"Het veld :guilabel:`JoFotara-status` op het tabblad :guilabel:`Overige "
"informatie` van bevestigde verkoopfacturen geeft de huidige status van het "
"document in JoFotara weer. Het kan handmatig worden gewijzigd om de "
"werkelijke status van de verkoopfacturen weer te geven in gevallen waarin "
"een technische fout of time-out voorkomt dat Odoo deze automatisch bijwerkt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:219
msgid "Validating QR codes (Sanad app)"
msgstr "QR-codes valideren (Sanad-app)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:221
msgid ""
"To validate the QR code received from JoFotara on the invoice, follow these "
"steps:"
msgstr ""
"Volg deze stappen om de QR-code te valideren die je van JoFotara op de "
"verkoopfactuur hebt ontvangen:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:223
msgid "Install the `Sanad app <https://www.sanad.gov.jo/Default/en>`_."
msgstr "Installeer de `Sanad-app <https://www.sanad.gov.jo/Default/en>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:224
msgid "Navigate to :guilabel:`More`."
msgstr "Ga naar :guilabel:`Meer`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:225
msgid "Click on :guilabel:`Validate document` and scan the QR code."
msgstr "Klik op :guilabel:`Document valideren` en scan de QR-code."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:226
msgid "Review results."
msgstr "Bekijk de resultaten."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:233
msgid ""
"To send a debit or credit note to JoFotara, first create the :ref:`debit "
"<accounting/credit_notes/issue-debit-note>` or :ref:`credit note <accounting/"
"credit_notes/issue-credit-note>`. In the :guilabel:`Send` window, "
"click :guilabel:`JoFotara (Jordan EDI)` to submit it for real-time "
"validation. Upon successful validation, the QR code from JoFotara is "
"embedded in the debit or credit note PDF."
msgstr ""
"Om een debet- of creditfactuur naar JoFotara te verzenden, maak je eerst de "
":ref:`debetfactuur <accounting/credit_notes/issue-debit-note>` of "
":ref:`creditfactuur <accounting/credit_notes/issue-credit-note>`. Klik in "
"het venster :guilabel:`Verzenden` op :guilabel:`JoFotara (Jordaanse EDI)` om "
"deze in te dienen voor realtimevalidatie. Na succesvolle validatie wordt de "
"QR-code van JoFotara ingesloten in de pdf van de debet- of creditfactuur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:240
msgid ""
"Ensure that the :guilabel:`Reason` for generating a debit/credit note aligns "
"with ISTD regulations."
msgstr ""
"Zorg ervoor dat de :guilabel:`Reden` voor het genereren van een debet-/"
"creditfactuur aansluit bij de ISTD-regelgeving."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:246
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:626
msgid "Discounts"
msgstr "Kortingen"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:248
msgid ""
"JoFotara does not support negative quantities or negative prices on invoice "
"lines. As a result, global discount and fixed amount discount functionality "
"are not supported."
msgstr ""
"JoFotara ondersteunt geen negatieve hoeveelheden of negatieve prijzen op "
"factuurregels. Hierdoor worden algemene korting en kortingsfunctionaliteit "
"met vast bedrag niet ondersteund."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:251
msgid ""
"Discounts must be applied **per invoice line as a percentage** instead of as "
"a global discount or fixed amount."
msgstr ""
"Kortingen moeten **per factuurregel als percentage** worden toegepast in "
"plaats van als algemene korting of vast bedrag."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:255
msgid ""
"Attempting to submit invoices to JoFotara with negative invoice lines will "
"result in validation errors."
msgstr ""
"Pogingen om verkoopfacturen met negatieve factuurregels naar JoFotara te "
"verzenden, leiden tot validatiefouten."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:259
msgid ":ref:`Discount types <sales/discounts/discount-button>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Kortingstypes <sales/discounts/discount-button>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:3
msgid "Kenya"
msgstr "Kenia"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:10
msgid ""
"Install the 🇰🇪 **Kenyan** :ref:`fiscal localization package "
"<fiscal_localizations/packages>` to get all the features of the Kenyan "
"localization."
msgstr ""
"Installeer het 🇰🇪 **Keniaanse** :ref:`fiscale localisatiepakket "
"<fiscal_localizations/packages>` om alle functies van de Keniaanse "
"lokalisatie te krijgen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:14
msgid "eTIMS"
msgstr "eTIMS"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:16
msgid ""
"The `Kenya Revenue Authority (KRA) <https://www.kra.go.ke/>`_ has "
"implemented the `electronic Tax Invoice Management System (eTIMS) <https://"
"www.kra.go.ke/online-services/etims>`_ for tax collection."
msgstr ""
"De `Kenya Revenue Authority (KRA) <https://www.kra.go.ke/>`_ heeft het "
"`electronic Tax Invoice Management System (eTIMS) <https://www.kra.go.ke/"
"online-services/etims>`_ geïmplementeerd voor belastinginning."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:20
msgid ""
"To submit documents through eTIMS, you must use an :abbr:`OSCU (Online Sales "
"Control Unit)` that integrates with the existing **Trader Invoicing System "
"(TIS)**, such as the one provided by Odoo. The OSCU is used to validate, "
"encrypt, sign, transmit, and store tax invoices."
msgstr ""
"Om documenten via eTIMS in te dienen, moet je een :abbr:`OSCU (Online Sales "
"Control Unit)` gebruiken die integreert met het bestaande **Trader Invoicing "
"System (TIS)**, zoals die van Odoo. De OSCU wordt gebruikt om "
"belastingfacturen te valideren, versleutelen, ondertekenen, verzenden en "
"opslaan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:25
msgid ""
"Make sure to :ref:`install <general/install>` the **Kenya eTIMS EDI** "
"modules to use the OSCU device fully."
msgstr ""
"Zorg ervoor dat je de **Kenya eTIMS EDI**-modules :ref:`installeert <general/"
"install>` om het OSCU-apparaat volledig te gebruiken."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:31
msgid "OSCU device initialization"
msgstr "Initialisatie OSCU-apparaat"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:33
msgid ""
"The OSCU must be initialized before use. To do so, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Settings --> General Settings`, click :guilabel:`Update "
"Info` in the :guilabel:`Companies` section, and enter your :guilabel:`Tax "
"ID`."
msgstr ""
"De OSCU moet vóór gebruik worden geïnitialiseerd. Ga hiervoor naar "
":menuselection:`Instellingen --> Algemene instellingen`, klik op "
":guilabel:`Info bijwerken` in het gedeelte :guilabel:`Bedrijven` en voer je "
":guilabel:`Btw-nummer` in."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:37
msgid "To initialize the OSCU:"
msgstr "Om de OSCU te initialiseren:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:39
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Settings --> General Settings` and scroll down to "
"the :guilabel:`Kenya eTIMS Integration` section."
msgstr ""
"Ga naar :menuselection:`Instellingen --> Algemene instellingen` en scroll "
"naar beneden naar het gedeelte :guilabel:`Kenya eTIMS-integratie`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:41
msgid ""
"Set the :guilabel:`eTIMS Server Mode` to :guilabel:`Test` for the "
"initialization."
msgstr ""
"Stel de :guilabel:`eTIMS-servermodus` in op :guilabel:`Test` voor de "
"initialisatie."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:42
msgid ""
