#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/luxembourg.rst:65
msgid ""
"intra-community VAT: applied to goods and services sold to or purchased from "
"VAT-registered persons located in other EU countries"
msgstr ""
"intracommunautaire btw: toegepast op goederen en diensten verkocht aan of "
