"entreprises/fiscalite/impots-benefices/tva/declarations/declaration-tva.html>"
"`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/luxembourg.rst:251
msgid ""
"`Platform for electronic gathering of financial data (eCDF) <http://"
"www.ecdf.lu>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Platform voor elektronisch verzamelen van financiële gegevens (eCDF) "
