#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:205
msgid "EFT batch payments"
msgstr "EFT-batchbetalingen"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:207
msgid ""
"An :abbr:`EFT (electronic funds transfer)` batch file is a digital format "
"used to facilitate bulk payment processing for businesses. It allows "
"companies to consolidate multiple inbound and outbound payments into a "
"single electronic file. This process is commonly used by businesses handling "
"multiple payments at once, such as payroll or payments to multiple suppliers."
msgstr ""
"Een :abbr:`EFT (electronic funds transfer)` batchbestand is een digitaal "
"formaat dat wordt gebruikt om bulkbetalingsverwerking voor bedrijven te "
"vergemakkelijken. Het stelt bedrijven in staat om meerdere inkomende en "
"uitgaande betalingen te consolideren in één elektronisch bestand. Dit proces "
"wordt vaak gebruikt door bedrijven die meerdere betalingen tegelijk "
"verwerken, zoals loonadministratie of betalingen aan meerdere leveranciers."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:219
msgid ""
":ref:`Install <general/install>` the :guilabel:`EFT Batch Payment` module "
"(`l10n_nz_eft`)."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Installeer <general/install>` de module :guilabel:`EFT Batchbetaling` "
"(`l10n_nz_eft`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:220
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings`. In "
"the :guilabel:`Customer Payments` section, enable :guilabel:`Batch Payments`."
msgstr ""
"Ga naar :menuselection:`Boekhouding --> Configuratie --> Instellingen`. "
"Schakel in de sectie :guilabel:`Klantbetalingen` de optie "
":guilabel:`Batchbetalingen` in."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:224
msgid ":doc:`../../../applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../../applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:231
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Journals` to "
"configure the bank **journal**. In the :guilabel:`Journal Entries` tab, "
"enter the :guilabel:`Account Number` and click :guilabel:`Create and "
"edit...`. In the :guilabel:`Create Account Number` window, fill in "
"the :guilabel:`Bank` and enable :guilabel:`Send Money` to set the bank "
"account as trusted. The :guilabel:`Currency` field is optional."
msgstr ""
"Ga naar :menuselection:`Boekhouding --> Configuratie --> Dagboeken` om het "
"bank**dagboek** te configureren. Voer in het tabblad :guilabel:`Boekingen` "
"het :guilabel:`Rekeningnummer` in en klik op :guilabel:`Aanmaken en "
"bewerken...`. Vul in het venster :guilabel:`Rekeningnummer aanmaken` de "
":guilabel:`Bank` in en schakel :guilabel:`Geld verzenden` in om de "
"bankrekening als vertrouwd in te stellen. Het veld :guilabel:`Valuta` is "
"optioneel."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:240
msgid "Contacts' bank accounts"
msgstr "Bankrekeningen van contacten"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:242
msgid ""
"To add banking information for a contact, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> "
"Customers`, :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> Vendors`, or access "
"the contact directly through the **Contacts** app. Select the relevant "
"contact, then open the :guilabel:`Accounting` tab. Under the :guilabel:`Bank "
"Accounts` section, click :guilabel:`Add a line` to enter the required "
"details."
msgstr ""
"Om bankinformatie voor een contact toe te voegen, navigeer je naar "
":menuselection:`Boekhouding --> Klanten --> Klanten`, "
":menuselection:`Boekhouding --> Leveranciers --> Leveranciers`, of open het "
"contact rechtstreeks via de app **Contacten**. Selecteer het relevante "
"contact en open vervolgens het tabblad :guilabel:`Boekhouding`. Klik onder "
"de sectie :guilabel:`Bankrekeningen` op :guilabel:`Regel toevoegen` om de "
"vereiste gegevens in te voeren."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:250
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Account Holder` (it will automatically be selected for that "
"contact)"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Rekeninghouder` (wordt automatisch geselecteerd voor dat contact)"

