msgid ""
"Next, click :guilabel:`Onboard Journal`. In the dialog box, providing "
"an :abbr:`OTP (one-time password)` code is required. To retrieve it, open "
"the `Fatoora simulation portal <https://fatoora.zatca.gov.sa/>`_, "
"click :guilabel:`Onboard New Solution Unit/Device`, choose the number of OTP "
"codes to generate (one per journal to configure), and "
