"Enable :guilabel:`Stop automatic sending to tax authorities` "
"and :guilabel:`Default for built-in API` based on preference."
msgstr ""
"Schakel :guilabel:`Automatisch verzenden naar belastingdienst stoppen` en "
":guilabel:`Standaard voor ingebouwde API` in op basis van voorkeur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:135
msgid "Invoice issuance notice"
msgstr "Kennisgeving van factuuruitgifte"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:137
msgid ""
"On the left side of the main screen, in the :guilabel:`Release management` "
"menu, click :guilabel:`Create issuance notice` and follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Klik aan de linkerkant van het hoofdscherm in het menu "
":guilabel:`Uitgiftebeheer` op :guilabel:`Uitgiftekennisgeving aanmaken` en "
"volg deze stappen:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:140
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Add new`, select the :guilabel:`Name of the business unit "
"to issue an e-invoice` and the :guilabel:`Tax agency name`. Based on the "
"business unit and tax agency selected, the :guilabel:`Tax "
"code`, :guilabel:`Address`, :guilabel:`Phone number`, "
"and :guilabel:`Separator used` are automatically filled and uneditable."
msgstr ""
"Klik op :guilabel:`Nieuwe toevoegen`, selecteer de :guilabel:`Naam van de "
"bedrijfseenheid om een e-factuur uit te geven` en de :guilabel:`Naam "
"belastingdienst`. Op basis van de geselecteerde bedrijfseenheid en "
"belastingdienst worden de :guilabel:`Belastingcode`, :guilabel:`Adres`, "
":guilabel:`Telefoonnummer` en :guilabel:`Gebruikt scheidingsteken` "
"automatisch ingevuld en zijn niet bewerkbaar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:144
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Select the invoice type for issuance`, and then select and "
"fill in the following information :"
msgstr ""
"Klik op :guilabel:`Selecteer het factuurtype voor uitgifte` en selecteer en "
"vul vervolgens de volgende informatie in:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:147
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Invoice type`: The invoice type on which to declare an issuance "
"notice."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Factuurtype`: het factuurtype waarop een uitgiftekennisgeving "
"moet worden aangegeven."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:148
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Invoice template`: Select from the list of templates available "
"based on the invoice type."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Factuursjabloon`: selecteer uit de lijst met beschikbare "
"sjablonen op basis van het factuurtype."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:150
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Symbol`: Select from the list of symbols available based on the "
"invoice type."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Symbool`: selecteer uit de lijst met beschikbare symbolen op "
"basis van het factuurtype."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:151
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Quantity`: Total number of invoices to issue for the selected "
"type. Based on the type and template selected, this field is filled in "
"automatically. It can be changed if needed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Hoeveelheid`: totaal aantal uit te geven verkoopfacturen voor het "
"geselecteerde type. Op basis van het geselecteerde type en sjabloon wordt "
"dit veld automatisch ingevuld. Het kan indien nodig worden gewijzigd."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:153
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Start date of use`: The date from which the invoice template, "
"range, and quantity are used for the issuance notice."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Startdatum van gebruik`: de datum vanaf wanneer het "
"factuursjabloon, bereik en hoeveelheid worden gebruikt voor de "
"uitgiftekennisgeving."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:156
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Save` and select more invoice types if necessary by "
"repeating the steps above. Click :guilabel:`Save` to finish drafting the "
"notice."
msgstr ""
"Klik op :guilabel:`Opslaan` en selecteer indien nodig meer factuurtypen door "
"de bovenstaande stappen te herhalen. Klik op :guilabel:`Opslaan` om het "
"opstellen van de kennisgeving te voltooien."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:158
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Send to tax authorities` for approval. Once approved, the "
"notice's :guilabel:`Status` is changed to :guilabel:`Active`."
msgstr ""
"Klik op :guilabel:`Verzenden naar belastingdienst` voor goedkeuring. Na "
"goedkeuring wordt de :guilabel:`Status` van de kennisgeving gewijzigd in "
":guilabel:`Actief`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:164
msgid "Odoo database"
msgstr "Odoo-database"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:167
msgid "Link Odoo to SInvoice"
msgstr "Koppel Odoo aan SInvoice"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:169
msgid ""
"To connect Odoo with SInvoice, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`. In the :guilabel:`Vietnamese Integration` "
"section, fill in your SInvoice :guilabel:`Username` "
"and :guilabel:`Password`. Add a :guilabel:`Default symbol` to generate a "
"prefix for the invoice number managed in SInvoice if needed."
msgstr ""
"Ga naar :menuselection:`Boekhouding --> Configuratie --> Instellingen` om "
"Odoo te verbinden met SInvoice. Vul in het gedeelte :guilabel:`Vietnamese "
"Integration` je SInvoice :guilabel:`Username` en :guilabel:`Password` in. "
"Voeg indien nodig een :guilabel:`Default symbol` toe om een voorvoegsel te "
"genereren voor het factuurnummer dat wordt beheerd in SInvoice."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:175
msgid "Invoice template"
msgstr "Factuursjabloon"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:177
msgid ""
"To create SInvoice templates, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Templates`. Click :guilabel:`New` and add "
"a :guilabel:`Template code` and a :guilabel:`Template Invoice Type`. "
"The :guilabel:`Template code` is the initial sequence of digits in the name "
"assigned by SInvoice. For example, if the invoice template is `1/001 - Hóa "
"đơn GTGT - ND123`, the :guilabel:`Template code` is `1/001`. The SInvoice "
"templates in Odoo must match the ones in SInvoice."
msgstr ""
"Ga naar :menuselection:`Boekhouding --> Configuratie --> Templates` om "
"SInvoice-sjablonen te maken. Klik op :guilabel:`Nieuw` en voeg een "
":guilabel:`Template code` en een :guilabel:`Template Invoice Type` toe. De "
":guilabel:`Template code` is de eerste reeks cijfers in de naam die door "
"SInvoice is toegewezen. Als het factuursjabloon bijvoorbeeld `1/001 - Hóa "
"đơn GTGT - ND123` is, dan is de :guilabel:`Template code` `1/001`. De "
"SInvoice-sjablonen in Odoo moeten overeenkomen met die in SInvoice."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:183
msgid "To add :guilabel:`Invoice Symbols`, click :guilabel:`Add a new line`."
msgstr ""
"Klik op :guilabel:`Add a new line` om :guilabel:`Invoice Symbols` toe te "
"voegen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:186
msgid "Sending invoices to SInvoice"
msgstr "Verkoopfacturen verzenden naar SInvoice"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:188
msgid ""
"Invoices can be sent to SInvoice once they have been confirmed. To do so, "
"follow the :ref:`invoice sending <accounting/invoice/sending>` steps. In the "
"popup window, enable :guilabel:`Send to SInvoice` and click :guilabel:`Send`."
msgstr ""
"Verkoopfacturen kunnen naar SInvoice worden verzonden zodra ze zijn "
"bevestigd. Volg hiervoor de stappen voor het :ref:`versturen van facturen "
"<accounting/invoice/sending>`. Schakel in het pop-upvenster :guilabel:`Naar "
"SInvoice verzenden` in en klik op :guilabel:`Verzenden`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:192
msgid ""
"Once the invoice has been successfully submitted to SInvoice, "
"the :guilabel:`SInvoice Status` field in the :guilabel:`SInvoice` tab of the "
"invoice is updated to :guilabel:`Sent`. The :guilabel:`SInvoice "
"Number`, :guilabel:`Issue Date`, :guilabel:`Secret Code` "
"and :guilabel:`eInvoice Number` fields are also updated. The same "
"information is available on SInvoice."
msgstr ""
"Zodra de factuur succesvol is ingediend bij SInvoice, wordt het veld "
":guilabel:`SInvoice Status` op het tabblad :guilabel:`SInvoice` van de "
"factuur bijgewerkt naar :guilabel:`Sent`. De velden :guilabel:`SInvoice "
"Number`, :guilabel:`Issue Date`, :guilabel:`Secret Code` en "
":guilabel:`eInvoice Number` worden ook bijgewerkt. Dezelfde informatie is "
"beschikbaar op SInvoice."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:198
msgid "Replacement or adjustment invoices"
msgstr "Vervangende of correctiefacturen"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:200
msgid ""
"A replacement invoice is issued to correct an invoice that has **yet to be "
"tax declared**, whereas an adjustment invoice is issued to correct one that "
"has **already been tax declared**. Follow these steps to issue a replacement "
"or adjustment invoice:"
msgstr ""
"Een vervangende factuur wordt uitgegeven om een factuur te corrigeren die "
"**nog niet is aangegeven voor btw**, terwijl een correctiefactuur wordt "
"uitgegeven om een factuur te corrigeren die **al is aangegeven voor btw**. "
"Volg deze stappen om een vervangende of correctiefactuur uit te geven:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:204
msgid "Open the invoice and click :guilabel:`Credit Note`."
msgstr "Open de factuur en klik op :guilabel:`Credit Note`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:205
msgid "In the :guilabel:`Credit Note` popup, fill in the following fields:"
msgstr "Vul in de pop-up :guilabel:`Credit Note` de volgende velden in:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:207
msgid ":guilabel:`Reason displayed on Credit Note`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Reason displayed on Credit Note`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:208
msgid ":guilabel:`Adjustment type`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Adjustment type`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:209
msgid ":guilabel:`Agreement Name`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Agreement Name`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:210
msgid ":guilabel:`Agreement Date`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Agreement Date`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:211
msgid ":guilabel:`Journal`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Melding`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:212
msgid ":guilabel:`Reversal date`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Reversal date`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:214
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Reverse and Create Invoice` to issue a replacement invoice, "
"or :guilabel:`Reverse` to issue an adjustment invoice."
msgstr ""
"Klik op :guilabel:`Reverse and Create Invoice` om een vervangende factuur "
"uit te geven, of op :guilabel:`Reverse` om een correctiefactuur uit te geven."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:217
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`SInvoice Status` in the :guilabel:`SInvoice` invoice tab is "
"updated to :guilabel:`Replaced` for a replacement invoice "
"or :guilabel:`Adjusted` for an adjustment invoice."
msgstr ""
"De :guilabel:`SInvoice Status` op het factuurtabblad :guilabel:`SInvoice` "
"wordt bijgewerkt naar :guilabel:`Replaced` voor een vervangende factuur of "
"naar :guilabel:`Adjusted` voor een correctiefactuur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:223
msgid ""
"If an invoice needs to be canceled, open the invoice and "
"click :guilabel:`Request Cancel`. In the :guilabel:`Invoice Cancellation` "
"popup, enter the cancellation :guilabel:`Reason`, :guilabel:`Agreement "
"Name`, and :guilabel:`Agreement Date`, and click :guilabel:`Request "
"Cancellation`."
msgstr ""
"Als een factuur moet worden geannuleerd, open je de factuur en klik je op "
":guilabel:`Request Cancel`. Voer in de pop-up :guilabel:`Invoice "
"Cancellation` de :guilabel:`Reason`, :guilabel:`Agreement Name` en "
":guilabel:`Agreement Date` voor annulering in en klik op :guilabel:`Request "
"Cancellation`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:228
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`SInvoice Status` in the :guilabel:`SInvoice` invoice tab is "
"updated to :guilabel:`Canceled`."
msgstr ""
"De :guilabel:`SInvoice Status` in het :guilabel:`SInvoice` factuurtabblad is "
"bijgewerkt naar :guilabel:`Canceled`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:234
msgid "QR banking codes"
msgstr "QR-bankierenscodes"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:236
msgid ""
"Vietnamese QR banking is a payment service platform that allows customers to "
"make instant domestic payments to individuals and merchants in Vietnamese "
"dong via online and mobile banking."
msgstr ""
"Vietnamees QR-bankieren is een betalingsserviceplatform waarmee klanten "
"directe binnenlandse betalingen kunnen doen aan individuen en handelaren in "
"Vietnamese dong via online en mobiel bankieren."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:242
msgid ""
"To activate QR banking codes, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Settings` and enable :guilabel:`QR Codes` in "
"the :guilabel:`Customer Payments` section."
msgstr ""
"Activeer QR-codes via :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> "
"Settings` en schakel :guilabel:`QR Codes` in bij het gedeelte "
":guilabel:`Customer Payments`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:246
msgid "Bank account"
msgstr "Bankrekening"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:248
msgid ""
"To activate QR banking for a bank account, go to :menuselection:`Contacts --"
"> Configuration --> Bank Accounts` and select the bank account. Fill in "
"the :guilabel:`Bank Identifier Code`, :guilabel:`Proxy Type` (based on the "
"information used to identify the :guilabel:`Merchant Account`, such as the "
"card number and bank account numbers), and :guilabel:`Proxy Value` fields."
msgstr ""
"Activeer QR-bankieren voor een bankrekening via :menuselection:`Contacts --> "
"Configuration --> Bank Accounts` en selecteer de bankrekening. Vul de velden "
":guilabel:`Bank Identifier Code`, :guilabel:`Proxy Type` (gebaseerd op de "
"informatie die wordt gebruikt om de :guilabel:`Merchant Account` te "
"identificeren, zoals het kaartnummer en bankrekeningnummers) en "
":guilabel:`Proxy Value` in."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:253
msgid ""
"Enable :guilabel:`Include Reference` to include the invoice number in the QR "
"code."
msgstr ""
"Schakel :guilabel:`Include Reference` in om het factuurnummer in de QR-code "
"op te nemen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:256
msgid ""
"The account holder's country must be set to `Vietnam`, and their city must "
"be specified on the contact form."
msgstr ""
"Het land van de rekeninghouder moet zijn ingesteld op `Vietnam` en hun stad "
"moet worden gespecificeerd op het contactformulier."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:258
msgid ""
"The :ref:`account number <accounting/journals/bank>` and bank must be set on "
"the :guilabel:`Bank` journal."
msgstr ""
"Het :ref:`rekeningnummer <accounting/journals/bank>` en de bank moeten "
"worden ingesteld op het :guilabel:`Bank` dagboek."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:265
msgid "Generating QR codes on invoices"
msgstr "QR-codes genereren op facturen"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:267
msgid ""
"When creating a new invoice, open the :guilabel:`Other Info` tab and "
"select :guilabel:`EMV Merchant-Presented QR-code` in the :guilabel:`Payment "
"QR-code` field."
msgstr ""
"Open bij het aanmaken van een nieuwe factuur het tabblad :guilabel:`Other "
"Info` en selecteer :guilabel:`EMV Merchant-Presented QR-code` in het veld "
":guilabel:`Payment QR-code`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:271
msgid ""
"Ensure the :guilabel:`Recipient Bank` is configured, as Odoo uses this field "
"to generate QR codes."
msgstr ""
"Zorg ervoor dat de :guilabel:`Recipient Bank` is geconfigureerd, aangezien "
"Odoo dit veld gebruikt om QR-codes te genereren."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:28
msgid ""
"Odoo embeds several **payment providers** that allow your customers to pay "
"online, on their *customer portals*, or on your *eCommerce website*. They "
"can pay sales orders, invoices, or subscriptions with recurring payments "
"using their favorite payment methods, such as **credit cards**."
msgstr ""
"Odoo bevat verschillende **betaalproviders** waarmee je klanten online "
"kunnen betalen, op hun *klantportalen* of op je *e-commercewebsite*. Ze "
"kunnen verkooporders, facturen of abonnementen met terugkerende betalingen "
"betalen met hun favoriete betaalmethoden, zoals **creditcards**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:33
msgid ""
"Each payment provider is linked to a list of supported :ref:`payment methods "
"<payment_providers/payment_methods>` that can be (de)activated based on your "
"needs."
msgstr ""
"Elke betaalprovider is gekoppeld aan een lijst met ondersteunde "
":ref:`payment methods <payment_providers/payment_methods>` die kunnen worden "
"(de)geactiveerd op basis van je behoeften."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:None
msgid "Online payment form"
msgstr "Onlinebetalingsformulier"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:40
msgid ""
"Odoo apps delegate the handling of sensitive information to the certified "
"payment provider so that you don't ever have to worry about PCI compliance. "
"No sensitive information (such as credit card numbers) is stored on Odoo "
"servers or Odoo databases hosted elsewhere. Instead, Odoo apps use a unique "
"reference number for the data stored safely in the payment providers' "
"systems."
msgstr ""
"Odoo-apps delegeren de verwerking van gevoelige informatie aan de "
"gecertificeerde betaalprovider, zodat je je nooit zorgen hoeft te maken over "
"PCI-compliance. Geen gevoelige informatie (zoals creditcardnummers) wordt "
"opgeslagen op Odoo-servers of Odoo-databases die elders worden gehost. In "
"plaats daarvan gebruiken Odoo-apps een uniek referentienummer voor de "
"gegevens die veilig zijn opgeslagen in de systemen van de betaalproviders."

