msgid "Create an API user"
msgstr "Maak een API-gebruiker aan"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:16
msgid ""
"It is recommended to set up an **API user** to create transactions from Odoo "
"to ensure that your Worldline configuration remains safe even if credentials "
"are compromised. Additionally, API users do not require frequent password "
"updates like regular accounts."
msgstr ""
"Het is aanbevolen om een **API-gebruiker** in te stellen om transacties van "
"Odoo te maken, zodat je Worldline-configuratie veilig blijft, zelfs als "
"inloggegevens gecompromitteerd worden. Bovendien vereisen API-gebruikers "
"geen frequente wachtwoordupdates zoals gewone accounts."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:20
msgid "To create an **API user**, proceed as follows:"
msgstr "Volg de onderstaande stappen om een **API-gebruiker** aan te maken:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:22
msgid ""
"Log into your `Worldline Merchant Portal <https://merchant-portal.worldline-"
"solutions.com/>`_, click the :icon:`fa-th` (:guilabel:`menu`) icon, and "
"select :guilabel:`Back Office`."
msgstr ""
"Log in op je `Worldline Merchant Portal <https://merchant-portal.worldline-"
"solutions.com/>`_, klik op het :icon:`fa-th` (:guilabel:`menu`) icoon en "
"selecteer :guilabel:`Back Office`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:24
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Configuration --> Users` and click on :guilabel:`New "
"User`."
msgstr ""
"Ga naar :menuselection:`Configuration --> Users` en klik op :guilabel:`New "
"User`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:25
msgid "Configure the following fields:"
msgstr "Configureer de volgende velden:"

