msgstr ""
"Worldline moet nu geconfigureerd worden om betalingen van Odoo te accepteren."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:45
msgid ""
"From your merchant portal, go to :menuselection:`Developer --> Payment API` "
"and click on :guilabel:`Generate API key`. Copy the :guilabel:`API key ID` "
"and the :guilabel:`Secret API key` and save them for :ref:`later <wordline/"
"odoo-configuration>`."
msgstr ""
"Ga vanaf je merchant portal naar :menuselection:`Developer --> Payment API` "
"en klik op :guilabel:`Generate API key`. Kopieer de :guilabel:`API key ID` "
"en de :guilabel:`Secret API key` en bewaar ze voor :ref:`later <wordline/"
"odoo-configuration>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:48
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Developer --> Webhooks` and click "
"on :guilabel:`Generate webhook keys`. Copy the :guilabel:`Webhook ID` and "
"the associated :guilabel:`Secret webhook key` and save them for :ref:`later "
"<wordline/odoo-configuration>`."
msgstr ""
"Ga naar :menuselection:`Developer --> Webhooks` en klik op "
":guilabel:`Generate webhook keys`. Kopieer de :guilabel:`Webhook ID` en de "
"bijbehorende :guilabel:`Secret webhook key` en bewaar ze voor :ref:`later "
"<wordline/odoo-configuration>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:0
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Add webhook endpoint`, enter your Odoo database's URL "
"followed by `/payment/worldline/webhook` in the :guilabel:`Endpoint url` "
"field, and :guilabel:`Confirm`."
msgstr ""
"Klik op :guilabel:`Add webhook endpoint`, voer de URL van je Odoo-database "
"in gevolgd door `/payment/worldline/webhook` in het veld :guilabel:`Endpoint "
"url` en klik op :guilabel:`Confirm`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:0
